Comment_glosser: This seems like a mistake. 25 should either ‘æk kuɽi mɔ̃ɽɛ̃’,  which is  (1⋅20)+5′ or ‘mitˀ isi mɔ̃ɽɛ̃’, which is (1′⋅20′)+5′

This seems like a mistake. 25 should either ‘æk kuɽi irəl’,  which is  (1⋅20)+8′ or ‘mitˀ isi irəl’, which is (1′⋅20′)+8′
